<body>
    <h1>Semantic Clones (Similar Functions and Pattern Matches)</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h2 local-id=3D"a3762029aa52" id=3D"SemanticClones(SimilarFunctions=
andPatternMatches)-Purpose"><span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=
=3D"914144cf-54ca-418a-91ee-71b98e23fe66"><span class=3D"inline-comment-mar=
ker" data-ref=3D"70ce2b97-6a35-452a-91c3-705c56bac00a">Purpose</span></span=
></h2>
<p local-id=3D"ef72931ff222">The purpose of this subsystem is to attach sem=
antic meaning to indexed symbols so Bitloops can answer intent-level questi=
ons and <span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"c22dea3b-ee7d-409=
4-b66c-9d57dadcb1b4">retrieve semantically related artefacts</span></p>
<p local-id=3D"f0a32137e11a">For the MVP, this means:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"65469b76a41b">
<li local-id=3D"607d44d68a6b">
<p local-id=3D"42bb194156e7">identify <span class=3D"inline-comment-marker"=
 data-ref=3D"6316de8e-c0e1-4f43-90bb-09546aa3aafb">important symbols</span>=
 from parser-backed extraction</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fdbc10ffec7f">
<p local-id=3D"489b5262216b">attach a short semantic description to each sy=
mbol</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fcf621c160e1">
<p local-id=3D"ff61ea85dc2b">generate embeddings for semantic similarity</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"434add98550d">
<p local-id=3D"9b05300b3f85">combine semantic, lexical, and structural sign=
als to retrieve similar artefacts</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c10333b69dc8">
<p local-id=3D"1ff282d78819">expose explainable clone-like results such as =
similar implementations, exact duplicates, divergent forks, and preferred l=
ocal patterns</p></li>
</ul>
<h2 local-id=3D"e2ee012789a7" id=3D"SemanticClones(SimilarFunctionsandPatte=
rnMatches)-Goals"><span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"b82f199=
4-6945-4c2d-b336-f79ed608ec4a">Goals</span></h2>
<p local-id=3D"12994e7f3135"><span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=
=3D"c7168cfc-e27c-4dae-a90e-a88f4bc295cc">Add a semantic enrichment layer s=
o we can answer intent-level questions and retrieve clone-like neighbours w=
ith explainable scores:</span></p>
<ul local-id=3D"15245e4a91fa">
<li local-id=3D"9112a48b7909">
<p local-id=3D"4e0cfcd3454a">file or method purpose summaries</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d62fe9c6260d">
<p local-id=3D"695d4f140aa8">role/type labels for symbols</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cf66a8bed8e1">
<p local-id=3D"44ed9c42168b">semantically similar functions/modules</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"2e30a6d77ac8">
<p local-id=3D"839a88d634e4">exact duplicates and extraction candidates</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"88c4452f6244">
<p local-id=3D"99937cf76a46">divergent forks of formerly similar logic</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"9143110156fa">
<p local-id=3D"b6a5948bb97e">local "golden patterns" for a problem class</p=
></li>
</ul>
<h2 local-id=3D"bc391e423833" id=3D"SemanticClones(SimilarFunctionsandPatte=
rnMatches)-Non-goalsforthefirstiteration"><span class=3D"inline-comment-mar=
ker" data-ref=3D"0bf3d6b4-ff52-4597-8bcc-3f73ed73a826">Non-goals for the fi=
rst iteration</span></h2>
<ul local-id=3D"ffff4b512ce0">
<li local-id=3D"c43b9dceac52">
<p local-id=3D"6dd2bbc4849d">perfect <span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" =
data-ref=3D"f0477c8e-f5c5-4406-b781-57b591c743c1">clone</span> detection ac=
ross all languages</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"940c29f897d8">
<p local-id=3D"34d70f2a29c3"><span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=
=3D"7b5742c4-cd43-45a2-979b-dff7761d6bb2">cross-repo global embeddings</spa=
n></p></li>
</ul>
<h2 local-id=3D"13ff3d5a506d" id=3D"SemanticClones(SimilarFunctionsandPatte=
rnMatches)-Proposedarchitecture">Proposed architecture</h2>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">flowcha=
rt LR
    A["Pre-stage: structural extraction"] --&gt; B["Stage 1: semantics + re=
trieval features"]
    B --&gt; C["Stage 2: embeddings"]
    B --&gt; D["Stage 3: hybrid clone retrieval + reranking"]
    C --&gt; D
    D --&gt; E["symbol_clone_edges"]</pre>
</div>
</div><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper =
confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image im=
age-center" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"24aca414d546d7599b6015416=
016ea20103653850d3a3ade4de1bc3d8fff1100" data-image-src=3D"https://bitloops=
.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/432504852/image-20260310-164524.pn=
g?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1773161125922&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp=
;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"100" data-width=3D"809" data-unresolved-comment-c=
ount=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"436076545" data-linked-resource-versi=
on=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-defa=
ult-alias=3D"image-20260310-164524.png" data-base-url=3D"https://bitloops.a=
tlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-content-type=3D"image/png" data-lin=
ked-resource-container-id=3D"432504852" data-linked-resource-container-vers=
ion=3D"23" data-media-id=3D"d6a549f3-32a2-4af1-b3ad-a46c404fcf03" data-medi=
a-type=3D"file" height=3D"57"></span>
<h3 local-id=3D"c5ec027fa37c" id=3D"SemanticClones(SimilarFunctionsandPatte=
rnMatches)-Pipeline"><span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"8fa1=
c9ab-2aa0-485d-9ccb-e7d0b0a53d1a">Pipeline</span></h3>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"a489c2c79a22">
<li local-id=3D"9770d3dd5e53">
<p local-id=3D"eb64710f03a7"><span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=
=3D"15008d70-461f-4870-8629-acfafa5003cd">A pre-stage walks the parser/AST =
output and extracts normalized symbol structure. This is the artefact compl=
etion and Blast radius <a href=3D"https://bitloops.atlassian.net/wiki/space=
s/ADCP/pages/433946625/Artefact+Completion+and+Blast+Radius" data-linked-re=
source-id=3D"433946625" data-linked-resource-version=3D"16" data-linked-res=
ource-type=3D"page">stage</a>.</span></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cbedc75d4622">
<p local-id=3D"89e16ae94607">Stage 1 adds semantic summaries plus l<span cl=
ass=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"a08f914a-0df6-4f5a-a7c7-87da3a503=
e35">exical and structural retrieval features</span>.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8a009eff59b0">
<p local-id=3D"61010dc7d158">Stage 2 turns selected symbols into embeddings=
 and stores them in <code>pgvector/sqlite-vec</code>.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c56bdf3bd8fd">
<p local-id=3D"01ac4f7b5b36">Stage 3 uses semantic, lexical, and structural=
 signals to build explainable clone candidates and divergence signals.</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"840dff0daf09">
<p local-id=3D"32a9c10d83c3">Symbol clone edges done.</p></li>
</ol>
<h3 local-id=3D"5f052f9d4dfd" id=3D"SemanticClones(SimilarFunctionsandPatte=
rnMatches)-Whateachstagedoes">What each stage does</h3>
<h3 local-id=3D"e6f451c1d46e" id=3D"SemanticClones(SimilarFunctionsandPatte=
rnMatches)-Pre-stage:parser-backedstructuralextraction"><span class=3D"inli=
ne-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"6b137a6c-ba95-42a1-8bd9-5edfb75ea845">Pre-st=
age: parser-backed structural extraction</span></h3>
<h4 local-id=3D"cccd338961ca" id=3D"SemanticClones(SimilarFunctionsandPatte=
rnMatches)-Input:">Input:</h4>
<ul local-id=3D"cb34e5b9a578">
<li local-id=3D"59a401eb060d">
<p local-id=3D"ab94273ec19c">parser/AST output</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f348741df049">
<p local-id=3D"8b347c24aec1">file content and language metadata</p></li>
</ul>
<h4 local-id=3D"6f53cb788900" id=3D"SemanticClones(SimilarFunctionsandPatte=
rnMatches)-Output:">Output:</h4>
<ul local-id=3D"7cacf4d5fdd5">
<li local-id=3D"0592366cbabe">
<p local-id=3D"3a3467b4ad06">normalized symbol records</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7a9b0bbadadf">
<p local-id=3D"177720eee67d">parent-child relationships</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"634d39f526a0">
<p local-id=3D"f556dcf8e1e3">kind, name, path, line/byte ranges</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9a2bdf290625">
<p local-id=3D"b22e3dab7336">signatures, parent container</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"123f3d7cfaa3">
<p local-id=3D"d83141a85148">optional imports, annotations, inheritance, im=
plemented interfaces, and other structural context</p></li>
</ul>
<h4 local-id=3D"1eedb9328d95" id=3D"SemanticClones(SimilarFunctionsandPatte=
rnMatches)-Purpose:">Purpose:</h4>
<ul local-id=3D"4eec493788b5">
<li local-id=3D"f73b443f8e69">
<p local-id=3D"ef35fb12d17b">identify what symbols exist</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ac615f36997a">
<p local-id=3D"150dc504cc8e">capture their structure before any semantic la=
beling or vectorization happens</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8ae1c14cac1c">
<p local-id=3D"cfe3a626bca0">provide the raw material for later lexical, st=
ructural, and semantic analysis</p></li>
</ul>
<h4 local-id=3D"f9595d9aeed8" id=3D"SemanticClones(SimilarFunctionsandPatte=
rnMatches)-Importantdistinction:">Important distinction:</h4>
<ul local-id=3D"109e3676489a">
<li local-id=3D"74f93cb0c1e7">
<p local-id=3D"782369ccfd45"><span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=
=3D"d4df5598-46cc-423f-9843-7f7a0607f2d6">this step belongs to the parser/s=
ymbol extraction layer</span></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b8725b6922f5">
<p local-id=3D"d17ad4d227e6">it is not part of semantic summarization</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"449765e40bf4">
<p local-id=3D"aa0c4f062b6b">Stage 1 should assume these symbol records alr=
eady exist</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"4937508215e8" id=3D"SemanticClones(SimilarFunctionsandPatte=
rnMatches)-Stage1:semanticsummariespluslexical/structuralfeatureenrichment"=
>Stage 1: semantic summaries plus lexical/structural feature enrichment</h3=
>
<h4 local-id=3D"3f8303b2c7c7" id=3D"SemanticClones(SimilarFunctionsandPatte=
rnMatches)-Input:.1"><span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"af0e=
2d21-5068-4dc9-96a5-fd2f03166644">Input</span>:</h4>
<ul local-id=3D"d06e1484ea4b">
<li local-id=3D"a879302f212e">
<p local-id=3D"fad475976d17">normalized symbol records from the structural =
extraction step</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"274bebf86c24">
<p local-id=3D"14bb9e875215">optional docstrings/comments</p></li>
</ul>
<h4 local-id=3D"680fa0275a76" id=3D"SemanticClones(SimilarFunctionsandPatte=
rnMatches)-Output:.1"><span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"dc0=
a589e-875b-42d1-bab6-9474cb2e12f9">Output</span>:</h4>
<ul local-id=3D"f76cec25e6f4">
<li local-id=3D"c6531cb49b3e">
<p local-id=3D"9ac1aed98c55"><code>symbol_semantics.summary</code></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9c35095fdf05">
<p local-id=3D"5908cfcdfb4f"><code>symbol_semantics.confidence</code></p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"85dc434538af">
<p local-id=3D"cc4e644757ee">lexical features such as <span class=3D"inline=
-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"1d1b765d-b715-43b4-8c22-d8c59a393136">normaliz=
ed names, identifier tokens, normalized signatures, and normalized body tok=
ens</span></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c8b9840aca2c">
<p local-id=3D"0368b5aafd22">structural features <span class=3D"inline-comm=
ent-marker" data-ref=3D"4774aca4-9a32-43a9-88b4-13ea113c76dc">such as</span=
> parent kind, parameter count and local relationship/<span class=3D"inline=
-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"5cb28970-3d98-427d-9fac-6f05b3ceb60e">context =
metadata</span></p></li>
</ul>
<h4 local-id=3D"18a6f940942a" id=3D"SemanticClones(SimilarFunctionsandPatte=
rnMatches)-Howtheone-linesummaryisproduced:"><span class=3D"inline-comment-=
marker" data-ref=3D"bd4c2944-2521-4059-8098-9a9945c45fe3"><span class=3D"in=
line-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"284171f3-4b03-4071-a207-a3763c5b77e7">How =
the one-line summary is produced</span></span>:</h4>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"6e6fae15eec1">
<li local-id=3D"9841e79b1165">
<p local-id=3D"9c6e44243574"><span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=
=3D"bb0e65fb-9195-46be-9c5e-a1a1916cb2c0">Use docstring or leading comment =
text if it is present and high confidence.</span></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0365d76e2521">
<p local-id=3D"1c099105a04d">Ask <span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data=
-ref=3D"33cd875a-220c-4861-addd-6ab9b295c13f">an LLM</span> for a one-line =
purpose summary using symbol context.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c7e82def3298">
<p local-id=3D"857c3cf695ab"><span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=
=3D"c9a7f39b-bf85-4e87-92f1-354e7d94766c">Template structure from kind + na=
me + signature</span>.</p></li>
</ol>
<h4 local-id=3D"e0ae7e454cfb" id=3D"SemanticClones(SimilarFunctionsandPatte=
rnMatches)-Examplesummarycascade:"><span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" da=
ta-ref=3D"2a57c704-57fc-43ee-9287-de9491f2ea36">Example summary cascade</sp=
an>:</h4>
<ul local-id=3D"5326d43a8db8">
<li local-id=3D"bed9f05f9971">
<p local-id=3D"b2b6a7303f86">docstring path: "Parses the DevQL pipeline int=
o execution stages."</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3fd6a33acbc2">
<p local-id=3D"66dbf3bcbb86">LLM path: "Filters artefacts in Postgres and o=
ptionally attaches chat history."</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fde93eedac87">
<p local-id=3D"d2d00caff569">Template structure path: "Async Rust function =
for Postgres artefact query handling."</p></li>
</ul>
<h4 local-id=3D"328666385f55" id=3D"SemanticClones(SimilarFunctionsandPatte=
rnMatches)-Purpose:.1"><span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"82=
ef59a2-539c-4372-937d-ee43a82725e4">Purpose</span>:</h4>
<ul local-id=3D"d1e143a1678c">
<li local-id=3D"06f7e4bdf242">
<p local-id=3D"0dc82daafb38"><span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=
=3D"966998c5-de66-4b02-8941-9dbfd2d5f0d8">give </span><span class=3D"inline=
-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"28e0f70b-159b-43af-aea9-e59d42ed4a12"><span cl=
ass=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"966998c5-de66-4b02-8941-9dbfd2d5f=
0d8">every important symbol </span></span><span class=3D"inline-comment-mar=
ker" data-ref=3D"966998c5-de66-4b02-8941-9dbfd2d5f0d8">a short human-readab=
le purpose label</span></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9727ebafe43e">
<p local-id=3D"90233db3d41a"><span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=
=3D"99f4fa6a-69b0-4e8a-be2a-bf4728d03185">make responses understandable eve=
n without vector search</span></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d42afcc18834">
<p local-id=3D"b3750aefc76f"><span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=
=3D"b4b8ff8c-a62d-4d0f-9bc7-c4c00cc6a2fe">produce the lexical and structura=
l signals needed for hybrid retrieval</span></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a4d45c813b56">
<p local-id=3D"29b49cc5f7fa"><span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=
=3D"189cf0cc-b490-4f2d-95f9-41910bf82000">create better text inputs</span> =
for later embedding generation</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"10be56d4784c" id=3D"SemanticClones(SimilarFunctionsandPatte=
rnMatches)-Stage2:embeddingsinpgvector/sqlite-vec">Stage 2: embeddings in <=
code>pgvector/sqlite-vec</code></h3>
<h4 local-id=3D"5da419342750" id=3D"SemanticClones(SimilarFunctionsandPatte=
rnMatches)-Input:.2">Input:</h4>
<ul local-id=3D"c427a9d8fb75">
<li local-id=3D"a44defb7ec9c">
<p local-id=3D"039abbc67ad6"><span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=
=3D"b7b75ff5-ec9a-455b-983b-f3dbeda55a9d">selected artefacts</span> from St=
age 1</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c4d7e024d6a4">
<p local-id=3D"8f44e9dba3c3">canonical embedding text built from <span clas=
s=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"fd148981-b77f-43f9-968f-8428d1af9dd=
7">kind, name, signature, body, path, parent container, and current summary=
</span></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8fd48988032d">
<p local-id=3D"b466a6d010f1">configured <span class=3D"inline-comment-marke=
r" data-ref=3D"bec38783-eca8-47da-80d1-44de1d47eb7b">embedding provider/mod=
el</span></p></li>
</ul>
<h4 local-id=3D"7ac927ea6478" id=3D"SemanticClones(SimilarFunctionsandPatte=
rnMatches)-Output:.2">Output:</h4>
<ul local-id=3D"c9b2ac51d1c6">
<li local-id=3D"ea96f38c2f94">
<p local-id=3D"15ca13719394"><code>symbol_embeddings.embedding</code></p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"25892f252514">
<p local-id=3D"4ded3ebb8561"><span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=
=3D"df9d5424-416f-4466-9d84-4628895bcdbb">model/provider/dimension</span> m=
etadata</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"092229fe693b">
<p local-id=3D"99e8af0f1ffd">input hash for incremental reuse</p></li>
</ul>
<h4 local-id=3D"756308a58bff" id=3D"SemanticClones(SimilarFunctionsandPatte=
rnMatches)-Purpose:.2">Purpose:</h4>
<ul local-id=3D"4a78e15bb284">
<li local-id=3D"b27a053033a1">
<p local-id=3D"4cda3c7bfdf5">place symbols into vector space so Bitloops ca=
n do semantic nearest-neighbour retrieval</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6ed3f41ffcde">
<p local-id=3D"4719722ee2dd">support "find similar symbols" even when names=
 differ</p></li>
</ul>
<h4 local-id=3D"58a72848f36f" id=3D"SemanticClones(SimilarFunctionsandPatte=
rnMatches)-Operationalnote:">Operational note:</h4>
<ul local-id=3D"3639f514d945">
<li local-id=3D"6b8bc89010da">
<p local-id=3D"e8c24fbaccff">this stage requires an embedding model source<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9ba6b0cba3cb">
<p local-id=3D"c4e0eb3ce15f">for hosted providers that means an API key and=
 provider configuration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7b980670e64d">
<p local-id=3D"46fb228cba09">for local providers such as Ollama that means =
a running local model endpoint<br></p></li>
</ul>
